reviewText: Just love the fact that I have this concert for my collection!  Not the best quality.  Could have been more to the concert but like I said just glad to have it!

Good news: here's your chance to see rare 1985 era Culture Club performing songs like God Thank You Woman and Gusto Blusto live in concert!

Bad news: this is basically an old vhs recording burned to dvd.  Picture quality is mediocre at best.
I enjoyed the concert. The dvd itself was not very clear,had it been it would have been perfect.
